from the other direction.

1:02:26.380 --> 1:02:28.182
Answer me, god damn it!

1:02:31.151 --> 1:02:33.120
Jessica? Honey?

1:02:35.055 --> 1:02:35.689
Stella?

1:02:36.724 --> 1:02:38.325
