1:03:31.612 --> 1:03:33.146
Jess?

1:03:33.180 --> 1:03:34.816
Oh my god, Jess?

1:04:03.176 --> 1:04:04.278
How you feeling?

1:04:05.847 --> 1:04:07.047
In any pain?

1:04:10.584 --> 1:04:11.518
You still cramping?

1:04:17.825 --> 1:04:20.828
Can I get you something
to eat? Are you hungry?

1:04:23.765 --> 1:04:28.770
I've got my dinner
right here.

1:04:32.339 --> 1:04:33.708
Jess.

1:04:33.741 --> 1:04:34.608
I love wine.

1:04:38.545 --> 1:04:40.314
I know you do.

1:04:40.347 --> 1:04:44.384
I love junk food and I
love wine and I love Stella.

1:04:48.856 --> 1:04:49.791
I love you.

1:04:52.359 --> 1:04:54.194
I love you, too, kiddo.

1:04:56.764 --> 1:04:58.298
And so does Stella.

1:04:58.332 --> 1:04:59.232
Don't say her name.

1:05:01.468 --> 1:05:02.302
Please.

1:05:07.574 --> 1:05:09.443
You're the best
person I know, Ali.

1:05:16.450 --> 1:05:19.419
You're one of the best
people I know too, Jess.

1:05:22.522 --> 1:05:23.357
One of.

1:05:26.693 --> 1:05:28.261
But not the best.

1:05:31.431 --> 1:05:33.567
I'm not the best
person you know either.

1:05:33.600 --> 1:05:34.869
Yes, you are.

1:05:34.902 --> 1:05:38.271
No.

1:05:38.305 --> 1:05:39.373
Stella's great.

1:05:39.406 --> 1:05:40.474
Stella's dead.

1:05:45.212 --> 1:05:46.279
We don't know that.

1:05:48.215 --> 1:05:48.850
I know.

1:05:50.885 --> 1:05:51.819
