1:05:53.988 --> 1:05:54.889
on the radio.

1:05:56.958 --> 1:06:02.162
She's dead, our baby's
dead, soon I'll be dead.

1:06:05.232 --> 1:06:07.300
- Jess.
- You, Derek-

1:06:07.334 --> 1:06:09.971
- Jess.
- Kevin.

1:06:10.004 --> 1:06:11.638
- Jess.
- And everybody.

1:06:16.510 --> 1:06:17.310
Jess.

1:06:19.013 --> 1:06:20.948
We were good together, Ali.

1:06:22.382 --> 1:06:24.451
We can be good again.

1:06:24.484 --> 1:06:26.286
I know you miss me.

1:06:26.319 --> 1:06:28.321
Jess, Jess.

1:06:31.425 --> 1:06:32.526
You're happily married.

1:06:33.961 --> 1:06:38.833
This isn't you, this is
just the stress, the fear.

1:06:39.734 --> 1:06:41.535
And oh, you're so worried-

1:06:42.804 --> 1:06:44.604
Jess, no.

1:06:44.638 --> 1:06:46.606
You wanna be with me, Ali,
I know you do, I can tell.

1:06:52.046 --> 1:06:53.715
But not like this.

1:06:58.485 --> 1:07:00.320
Then leave me alone.

1:07:01.388 --> 1:07:02.656
Jess.

1:07:02.689 --> 1:07:03.490
I said leave me
the fuck alone!

1:07:30.017 --> 1:07:31.651
How is she?

1:07:31.685 --> 1:07:34.722
Grieving,
emotionally fragile,

1:07:34.756 --> 1:07:36.758
despondent, hallucinating.

1:07:37.725 --> 1:07:38.558
Take your pick.

1:07:40.995 --> 1:07:42.329
Have you seen Derek?

1:07:44.564 --> 1:07:45.365
Kung fu grip.

1:07:46.566 --> 1:07:48.435
He's out patrolling
the perimeter

1:07:48.468 --> 1:07:50.805
making sure there's
no nut jobs out there.

1:07:50.838 --> 1:07:51.873
All right, well if you
see him will you tell him

1:07:51.906 --> 1:07:53.741
I need to talk to him?

1:07:55.375 --> 1:07:55.977
Please.

1:08:16.630 --> 1:08:17.464
Jess?

1:08:21.535 --> 1:08:22.602
Jessi?

1:08:25.505 --> 1:08:26.673
Jessi!

1:08:26.707 --> 1:08:27.541
Jessi!

1:08:28.542 --> 1:08:30.812
Jessi, Jessi, Jessi, Jessi!

1:08:38.953 --> 1:08:40.021
Come on, Derek, let's go.

1:08:40.054 --> 1:08:41.722
It's time to go look for Jess.

1:08:41.756 --> 1:08:42.556
Sun's up.

1:08:45.760 --> 1:08:47.728
Oh shit, I got her,
I got her, Kevin.

1:08:47.762 --> 1:08:48.595
Come on!

1:08:55.803 --> 1:08:57.839
Jessi, I'm coming!

1:08:57.872 --> 1:08:59.573
Get her out, get her out!

1:08:59.606 --> 1:09:00.607
Get her out!

1:09:05.579 --> 1:09:06.413
No, no!

1:09:15.622 --> 1:09:16.858
I can't, I can't!

1:09:17.925 --> 1:09:19.559
I can't!

1:09:19.593 --> 1:09:20.660
Ali!

1:09:20.694 --> 1:09:21.528
Ali!

1:09:47.154 --> 1:09:49.156
Oh, what the fuck, dude?

1:09:50.758 --> 1:09:53.060
She's got wounds on
her arms just like mine.

1:09:53.094 --> 1:09:55.462
Wounds you gave me
with that knife.

1:09:56.429 --> 1:09:58.465
The knife I just found
under Jessi's body.

1:09:59.566 --> 1:10:00.868
He killed her, Al.

1:10:00.902 --> 1:10:02.636
This sack of shit
murdered Jessi.

1:10:02.669 --> 1:10:06.539
Al, you said she was
despondent, hallucinating.

1:10:07.474 --> 1:10:09.710
You also called her
emotionally fragile.

1:10:09.744 --> 1:10:12.847
Are you seriously trying
to play this off as suicide?

1:10:12.880 --> 1:10:14.681
She was butchered!

1:10:14.715 --> 1:10:16.549
You don't know that.

1:10:16.583 --> 1:10:19.020
Maybe it was suicide,
maybe it was murder.

1:10:20.221 --> 1:10:21.688
I didn't do it.

1:10:21.722 --> 1:10:23.490
I haven't seen
that knife in days.

1:10:24.392 --> 1:10:26.693
No more lying,
you little fucker.

1:10:26.727 --> 1:10:28.095
Come on, man, don't do this.

1:10:28.129 --> 1:10:29.596
Don't do this.

1:10:29.629 --> 1:10:30.563
We don't know what's
in the lights.

1:10:31.698 --> 1:10:34.668
We've all looked
through the lights.

1:10:34.701 --> 1:10:36.938
We've all seen the lights,
they've changed us.

1:10:39.606 --> 1:10:42.243
We don't know, maybe
the lights did it.

1:10:42.276 --> 1:10:44.078
Enough with the lights!

1:10:45.780 --> 1:10:47.081
Enough!

1:10:47.114 --> 1:10:48.249
U.S. forces
have established

1:10:48.282 --> 1:10:50.751
multiple safe zones in the area.

1:10:50.785 --> 1:10:53.520
Secure transportation
from these safe zones,

1:10:53.553 --> 1:10:55.923
government-fortified
locations will be provided

1:10:55.957 --> 1:10:58.525
to any civilians requesting it.

1:10:58.558 --> 1:11:00.694
A convoy of transports
will disembark

1:11:00.728 --> 1:11:03.030
to location designated
Safe Zone Alpha

1:11:03.064 --> 1:11:05.766
at zero hundred hours
midnight local time.

1:11:05.800 --> 1:11:08.668
The convoy will then
proceed to the designated

1:11:08.702 --> 1:11:11.638
safe zone Bravo and Charlie.

1:11:11.671 --> 1:11:13.174
Departure time from Zone Bravo

1:11:13.207 --> 1:11:15.109
is oh-two hundred hours.

1:11:15.142 --> 1:11:18.212
Departure from Zone Charlie
will be oh-four hundred hours.

1:11:18.245 --> 1:11:20.247
CQ, CQ, CQ.

1:11:20.281 --> 1:11:21.949
Does anyone read?

1:11:21.983 --> 1:11:23.550
Departure
coordinates will immediately

1:11:23.583 --> 1:11:25.152
follow this message.

1:11:25.186 --> 1:11:29.556
Communication will repeat
indefinitely on this frequency.

1:11:33.995 --> 1:11:36.097
CQ, CQ, does anyone copy?

1:11:38.799 --> 1:11:41.168
CQ, CQ, CQ.

1:11:41.202 --> 1:11:44.537
Attention, this is a U.S.
armed forces broadcast

1:11:44.571 --> 1:11:46.639
from Fort Benning, Georgia
to surrounding localities.

1:11:46.673 --> 1:11:48.075
Damn it.

1:11:48.109 --> 1:11:49.977
Under direct
order of the Pentagon,

1:11:50.011 --> 1:11:52.813
global authorities,
National Guard,

1:11:52.847 --> 1:11:57.650
U.S. forces and-

1:12:05.059 --> 1:12:06.861
Just put back
what you took out.

1:12:06.894 --> 1:12:09.030
I already told you I
didn't take anything.

1:12:09.063 --> 1:12:10.731
Then where are
the parts, Einstein?

1:12:10.765 --> 1:12:12.233
I don't know
even if I had them.

1:12:12.266 --> 1:12:13.768
Look, it's a mess in here.

1:12:13.801 --> 1:12:15.302
The wires are
stripped, hose is cut.

1:12:16.170 --> 1:12:17.004
It ain't moving.

1:12:34.687 --> 1:12:37.590
I'm so sorry I
couldn't save you, Jessi.

1:12:41.896 --> 1:12:45.598
I love you. Always.

1:12:47.234 --> 1:12:48.936
You remember the
lights to save your ass,

1:12:48.969 --> 1:12:51.305
but you forget the parts
you stole from my SUV.

1:12:52.373 --> 1:12:57.745
Yeah, this memory loss seems a
little too convenient for me.

1:13:00.781 --> 1:13:05.219
Fuck you, Derek.

1:13:05.252 --> 1:13:07.088
What, you gonna shoot
me now, asshole?

1:13:07.121 --> 1:13:08.889
I don't need a gun

1:13:08.923 --> 1:13:11.358
- to prove a point, cocksucker.
- God damnit, stop it!

1:13:11.392 --> 1:13:13.294
What is wrong with you?

1:13:14.862 --> 1:13:16.263
This isn't gonna solve anything.

1:13:18.099 --> 1:13:20.901
We have to work together from

1:13:20.935 --> 1:13:22.870
where we are with what we have.

1:13:25.940 --> 1:13:27.007
Are you calm?

1:13:28.175 --> 1:13:29.743
Yeah, I'm calm.

1:13:33.247 --> 1:13:38.252
Kevin, go get the map and
bring it to the picnic table.

1:13:40.788 --> 1:13:41.889
Go, Kevin!

1:13:46.827 --> 1:13:47.660
Prick.

1:13:50.331 --> 1:13:51.165
God.

1:13:57.905 --> 1:13:59.672
We walk.

1:13:59.707 --> 1:14:01.842
We need to make it to
Safe Zone Alpha by midnight.

1:14:01.876 --> 1:14:03.978
What's that? 13 miles?

1:14:04.011 --> 1:14:05.779
It's closer to 14.

1:14:06.780 --> 1:14:09.750
The average person
walks four miles an hour.

1:14:09.783 --> 1:14:11.285
I could manage maybe three.

1:14:11.318 --> 1:14:13.020
Yeah, but that's
on flat open ground,

1:14:13.053 --> 1:14:16.123
this is steep and the
terrain gets really rough.

1:14:16.157 --> 1:14:18.292
Okay, let's say I
average half that.

1:14:18.325 --> 1:14:20.895
What's that? Nine hours?

1:14:20.928 --> 1:14:24.865
Which still gets us to
the deadline two hours past

1:14:24.899 --> 1:14:26.467
at the best.

1:14:26.500 --> 1:14:29.136
- Damn it.
- Now, Safe Zone Bravo

1:14:29.170 --> 1:14:30.905
has a two a.m. deadline.

1:14:30.938 --> 1:14:33.207
It's further away but the
terrain is a lot easier.

1:14:33.240 --> 1:14:35.376
Once we get outta the woods
it's all sloping hills

1:14:35.409 --> 1:14:36.977
and old farm roads.

1:14:37.011 --> 1:14:38.045
That's less cover.

1:14:38.078 --> 1:14:39.847
It'd leave us more exposed.

1:14:39.880 --> 1:14:41.815
Yeah, but we have a chance
at making the deadline.

1:14:42.917 --> 1:14:45.853
It's gonna be really tight,
but I think that we could

1:14:45.886 --> 1:14:46.987
do it if we leave within
the next hour or so.

1:14:47.021 --> 1:14:48.189
Let's get walking then.

1:14:49.823 --> 1:14:52.092
Alison and I will
head for Safe Zone Bravo.

1:14:52.126 --> 1:14:53.027
You go for Alpha.

1:14:53.961 --> 1:14:55.196
What? No fucking way.

1:14:55.229 --> 1:14:56.297
What about the
weirdos out there?

1:14:56.330 --> 1:14:57.298
You'll be fine, cottonballs.

1:14:59.400 --> 1:15:00.467
Ali, I thought we were
putting this stuff behind us.

1:15:00.501 --> 1:15:02.002
We were gonna be family again.

1:15:02.036 --> 1:15:04.438
Kev, this is not
punishment, it's-

1:15:04.471 --> 1:15:06.173
- It's redundancy.

1:15:06.207 --> 1:15:07.942
When the Alpha people
get transferred to Bravo,

1:15:07.975 --> 1:15:09.410
if we're not there yet,
you do everything you can

1:15:09.443 --> 1:15:11.912
to buy us extra time
before the bus leaves.

1:15:11.946 --> 1:15:13.514
Like what, Gimpy?

1:15:13.547 --> 1:15:15.182
You could sabotage the engine.

1:16:02.863 --> 1:16:03.464
Ali?

1:16:07.935 --> 1:16:08.535
Coming.

1:16:31.325 --> 1:16:34.561
- Al, it's-
- Just give me a second.

1:16:34.595 --> 1:16:35.429
Okay?

1:16:46.640 --> 1:16:48.242
This plan is shit.

1:16:48.275 --> 1:16:49.810
It's the plan we have.

1:16:51.011 --> 1:16:52.379
I know he doesn't trust me.

1:16:52.413 --> 1:16:54.081
That's why he won't
give me the shotgun.

1:16:54.114 --> 1:16:55.949
But I don't trust him,
and neither should you.

1:16:59.953 --> 1:17:00.621
Why don't you come
with me, we could-

1:17:00.654 --> 1:17:02.289
- Kev, don't.

1:17:04.058 --> 1:17:05.426
You don't trust me either.

1:17:07.127 --> 1:17:08.929
- Kevin, I haven't se-
- No, it's fine.

1:17:15.135 --> 1:17:16.937
You should know that
I remember Hanna.

1:17:18.339 --> 1:17:22.242
Sometimes. It's spotty like
a TV with bad reception.

1:17:23.344 --> 1:17:25.212
I know that I didn't kill her,

1:17:25.245 --> 1:17:27.848
just like I know that I
didn't sabotage the SUV.

1:17:29.116 --> 1:17:31.985
And if I didn't do
it, then who did?

1:17:36.590 --> 1:17:37.958
Ali?

1:17:39.360 --> 1:17:40.194
Coming.

1:17:45.399 --> 1:17:47.000
What about Jessi?

1:17:53.273 --> 1:17:55.142
I honestly don't remember.

1:18:04.184 --> 1:18:05.018
Bye, Kev.

1:18:06.019 --> 1:18:08.322
This isn't goodbye,
this is see you in a few.

1:18:09.423 --> 1:18:10.257
Right?

1:18:16.130 --> 1:18:16.930
Kevin.

1:18:27.074 --> 1:18:28.642
You be careful, okay?

1:18:30.611 --> 1:18:32.045
Yeah, you too.

1:19:41.248 --> 1:19:43.050
Ali, wait up.

1:19:53.427 --> 1:19:55.730
We were making pretty good time.

1:19:55.763 --> 1:19:57.364
I thought we could take a break.

1:20:08.475 --> 1:20:09.376
You've been quiet.

1:20:10.745 --> 1:20:12.646
I was just thinking
about something Kevin said.

1:20:14.314 --> 1:20:15.148
About the lights.

1:20:18.720 --> 1:20:20.120
How's your leg?

1:20:20.153 --> 1:20:21.522
Could use some aspirin.

1:20:21.555 --> 1:20:23.056
There's some in that pack.

1:20:33.333 --> 1:20:34.201
Car parts.

1:20:45.312 --> 1:20:46.547
Babe.

1:20:46.580 --> 1:20:48.115
You ok-

1:21:05.599 --> 1:21:06.433
Alison.

1:23:33.346 --> 1:23:37.250
Fuck, Ali.

1:23:37.284 --> 1:23:38.418
Holy shit.

1:23:38.452 --> 1:23:39.453
I heard a gun shot.

1:23:39.486 --> 1:23:40.822
Are you okay? Whoa!

1:23:40.855 --> 1:23:42.023
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

1:23:42.056 --> 1:23:43.457
Why, why, why?

1:23:43.490 --> 1:23:45.358
You murdered Derek.

1:23:45.392 --> 1:23:46.359
Probably Jessi, too!

1:23:47.527 --> 1:23:50.630
No, no, I was following you.

1:23:50.664 --> 1:23:54.769
I heard the gunshots, Ali.
We have to be careful.

1:23:54.802 --> 1:23:57.839
The horde, we have to be quiet.

1:23:57.872 --> 1:24:00.440
You were supposed to be
going the other direction.

1:24:01.876 --> 1:24:04.377
I didn't wanna
leave him alone with you, Ali.

1:24:11.418 --> 1:24:14.421
I don't know what's real.

1:24:14.454 --> 1:24:17.324
The horde, they're real.

1:24:19.526 --> 1:24:20.527
We're gonna be okay.

1:24:22.063 --> 1:24:23.731
We just have to
trust each other.

1:24:24.564 --> 1:24:25.465
Put the gun down.

1:24:29.536 --> 1:24:30.370
Yeah.

1:24:31.005 --> 1:24:32.339
We're family.

1:24:36.643 --> 1:24:40.547
You're lying.

1:24:40.580 --> 1:24:41.916
Maybe, but that's
the thing, Ali.

1:24:41.949 --> 1:24:46.620
Once you see the lights,
really see the lights,

1:24:46.653 --> 1:24:48.288
the truth, it doesn't matter.

1:24:49.924 --> 1:24:53.593
So get that fucking gun
out of my fucking face!

1:24:55.428 --> 1:24:56.563
We both know that
you're not gonna pull-

1:25:02.602 --> 1:25:05.006
